<c74object name="abc.gotoevent" module="abclib">
  <digest>Abclib's event counter utility</digest>
  <description><o>abc.gotoevent</o> abstraction enables to resume a mixed music piece at a certain event. Left input is the target as an event number, right input is the bang that triggers the counter from 0 to that event. It first switches off the dsp if it is on, and at the end restores its status as it was.
  <br /><br /></description>

